file.name: api.yaml
file.content:
openapi: 3.0.0
paths:
info:
  title:
  version:
components:
  schemas:
    EnumHolder:
      type: object
      properties:
        array_of_enums:
          type: array
          items:
            type: string
            x-extensible-enum:
              - array_enum_one
              - array_enum_two
        inlined_enum:
          type: string
          enum:
            - inlined_one
            - inlined_two
            - inlined_three
        inlined_extensible_enum:
          type: string
          x-extensible-enum:
            - inlined_one
            - inlined_two
            - inlined_three
        enum_ref:
          $ref: '#/components/schemas/EnumObject'
        extensible_enum_ref:
          $ref: '#/components/schemas/ExtensibleEnumObject'        
        list_enums:
          $ref: '#/components/schemas/ListEnums'

    EnumObject:
      type: string
      enum:
        - one
        - two
        - three

    ExtensibleEnumObject:
      type: string
      x-extensible-enum:
        - active
        - inactive
 
    ContentType:
      type: string
      x-extensible-enum:
        - application/json
        - application/x.some-type+json    
        - application/x.some-other-type+json;version=2    
          
    ListEnums:
      type: array
      items: 
        $ref: '#/components/schemas/ContentType'
